      "knowledge": "• Ionic, covalent (giant atomic), metallic, and layered covalent structures each produce a unique 3D arrangement of atoms or ions that explains all observable physical properties\n• The Gikomba four products (NaCl, graphite, diamond, copper wire) differ in behaviour because their bond types differ at the atomic level\n• Bond type → structure → physical property → real-world use is a complete explanatory chain for any solid material",
